The '''''Starflare''''' was the [[Yacht/Legends|space-yacht]] used by the [[Fel dynasty]] on [[Csilla/Legends|Csilla]] in around [[29 ABY/Legends|29 ABY]].

The Fels' daughter [[Wynssa Fel|Wynssa]] enjoyed taking the ''Starflare''{{'s}} helm, but she flew less often than she would have liked, due to the frequency with which her brother [[Cem Fel|Cem]] took the ship out. The name ''Starflare'' commemorated [[Baroness/Legends|Baroness]] [[Syal Antilles Fel]]'s former stage-name, "Wynssa Starflare," but it is not known what the yacht's capabilities were, or even whether she was built to a [[Chiss/Legends|Chiss]] or [[Human/Legends|Human]] design.

